OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,FA leaked report into the culture at
OL,7,FNorthumberland Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fdescribes a "culture of fear" at the
OL,9,Forganisation under the previous
OL,10,Fleadership, the Local Democracy
OL,11,FReporting Service reports.
OL,13,FThe review was commissioned over a
OL,14,Fyear ago after concerns were raised by
OL,15,Findividuals, but was never made public.
OL,17,FBoth the former chief and deputy were
OL,18,Fsuspended following the review last
OL,19,FMarch and later left the organisation.
OL,20,FReplacements for both positions are
OL,21,Fnow in place.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@]O]
