PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,FThe 35-page neutral report carried out
OL,7,Fby CMP Solutions said concerns about
OL,8,F"culture" at the fire service had
OL,9,Fresulted in "several staff booking on
OL,10,Fsick leave" and "threats of
OL,11,Fgrievances".
OL,13,FFrequently occurring themes raised by
OL,14,Fstaff included:
OL,16,FLeading officers were said to operate
OL,17,Fin a way that created "exclusion
OL,18,Frather than inclusion" and that they
OL,19,Fsought "conformity" and reacted
OL,20,F"negatively to any and all challenge".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]qD@MOUrD@KO]rD@QOUsD@KO]yD@
OL,26,AWOUzD@VO]{D@HOU{D@SO]|D@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
