FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,FThe level of funding for the service
OL,7,Fwas also said to have a negative
OL,8,Fimpact, particularly on staffing
OL,9,Flevels. A lack of "effective
OL,10,Fcommunications" was also criticised.
OL,12,FHowever, staff were also very positive
OL,13,Fabout their team environments.
OL,14,FOperational staff also "expressed
OL,15,Fpride in the service they provided to
OL,16,Fthe public and their operational
OL,17,Fcompetency".
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@OO]vD@XOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
