PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,FThe report set out a series of
OL,7,Frecommendations to improve the culture
OL,8,Fat the fire service. This included an
OL,9,F"inclusive, supportive" leadership
OL,10,Fthat is "open to challenge".
OL,12,FLevels of crewing and a review of
OL,13,Fworkloads at Fire Control was also
OL,14,Frecommended, as was a "complete
OL,15,Freview" of communications.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]rD@IOUrD@[O]vD@WOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
