PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,FResponding to the report, a spokesman
OL,7,Ffor Northumberland Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService said: "As part of building a
OL,9,Fclearer understanding of our culture,
OL,10,Fan independent review, or neutral
OL,11,Fassessment, was undertaken in early
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,F"Many staff contributed to this
OL,15,Fprocess and the report reflects
OL,16,Fcolleagues' experiences and
OL,17,Fperceptions at a particular point in
OL,18,Ftime, including areas of strength as
OL,19,Fwell as concerns.
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
