PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775751065
OL,3,CLeaked report describes 'culture of
OL,4,Cfear' at fire service
OL,6,F"The findings have helped inform our
OL,7,Fnew People & Culture Plan `
OL,8,Fstrengthening leadership and behaviour
OL,9,Fstandards, improving communication and
OL,10,Fengagement, reviewing promotion,
OL,11,Frecruitment and disciplinary
OL,12,Fapproaches to ensure fairness and
OL,13,Fconsistency and investing in
OL,14,Fwellbeing, inclusion and development.
OL,16,F"Work on these areas is already
OL,17,Funderway, with some actions taken
OL,18,Fimmediately following the findings."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
